Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:51.91,title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\frz358.26\1a&H7F&\frx6\fry338\pos(781,315)}{\c&H817F72&}鸦巢生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:51.91,title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz351.872\fad(0,200)\frx350\fry340\pos(785,577)}-休息-
